      </p>
      <p><bold><italic><tp:taxon-name obkms_id="b31a4ec0-1698-4bbd-92f6-9ddaa9647a0c" obkms_process="TRUE">Distephanus bara</tp:taxon-name></italic></bold>(Humbert) H. Rob., comb. nov. Basionym: <italic><tp:taxon-name obkms_id="71a490cf-14ba-4388-818b-a408b291f243" obkms_process="TRUE">Vernonia bara</tp:taxon-name></italic> Humbert, Notul. Syst. (Paris) 8: 9–10. 1939.
